<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="習禪" xml:id="gsz0771a17shiHengYue"><lb
ed="T" n="0771a17"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0771a17"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000028618">潭州翠微院</placeName><persName key="A010434">恒月</persName>傳<ptr target="#n1516"/>（<persName key="A010436">真亮</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0771a18"/><persName key="A010434">釋恒月</persName>，姓<name>韓</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000004130">上黨</placeName>人也。厥父為土<anchor xml:id="beg0771001"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>監</sic><corr>鹽</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0771001"/>商，<lb
ed="T" n="0771a19"/>西江往還，俄遇剽略溺死。<persName key="A010434">月</persName>雖幼弱，念父<lb
ed="T" n="0771a20"/>葬于魚腹，母又再行，乃決志出家，求報恩<lb
ed="T" n="0771a21"/>育。受教於<placeName key="PL000000023661">聖善寺</placeName><persName key="A010435">慧初</persName>。得度已，造<placeName key="PL000000023253">嵩山</placeName>禪會，<lb
ed="T" n="0771a22"/>便啟發心要。後訪道尋師，靡憚夷險，抵<placeName key="PL000000028618">望<lb
ed="T" n="0771a23"/>湖山翠微<anchor xml:id="beg0771sgsz1"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>嚴</sic><corr>巖</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0771sgsz1"/></placeName>下古院挂錫。四方學者如蜂得<lb
ed="T" n="0771a24"/>王，翕然<ptr type="glossary" target="#g768"/>盛化。<date key="j20059942006346" from-iso="+0780-02-15" to-iso="+0781-02-01"><name>建中</name>元年</date>，示疾而終，春秋七<lb
ed="T" n="0771a25"/>十九。<date key="j20060642006064" when-iso="+0780-04-25">其年三月十二日</date>遷塔焉。<placeName key="PL000000023549">洛京廣愛寺</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0771a26"/><persName key="A010436">釋真亮</persName>，姓<name>侯</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000003038">景城</placeName>人也。家訓儒雅，辭彩粲<lb
ed="T" n="0771a27"/>然。潔素持操，與群少年有異。忽以樊籠為<lb
ed="T" n="0771a28"/>厭，且曰：「去情除饉，是所願也。」遂於本州<placeName key="PL000000003233">開<lb
ed="T" n="0771a29"/>元寺</placeName><persName key="A010437">智休<roleName>師</roleName></persName>下披染服。然其刈薪汲水，率<pb ed="T" n="0771b" xml:id="T50.2061.0771b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0771b01"/>先於人，習行頭陀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g357"/>行。受具已，遊<placeName key="PL000000023255">嵩少</placeName>，遇<persName key="A009319">普<lb
ed="T" n="0771b02"/>寂</persName>獎訓，頓開蒙昧。入<placeName key="PL000000023647">龍門山</placeName>，居而禪默，問<lb
ed="T" n="0771b03"/>津者交集，聲望日隆。屬留守尚書<persName key="A008502">王<roleName>公</roleName><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>鐸</sic><corr>縉</corr></choice></persName><ptr target="#n1515"/>保<lb
ed="T" n="0771b04"/>釐<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1262"/>，聞而欽奉，召入<placeName key="PL000000023549">廣愛寺</placeName>，別住居焉。示人<lb
ed="T" n="0771b05"/>禪觀，匪倦教詔，得道者亦多矣。以<date key="j20092142009214" when-iso="+0788-12-09"><name>貞元</name>四<lb
ed="T" n="0771b06"/>年十一月三日</date>，忽告門人以桑榆<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1554"/>末照，誠<lb
ed="T" n="0771b07"/>難久留。囑累而終，年八十八焉。</p>
